Reflection
this activity highlighted how common security weaknesses still exist in everyday systems. it helped me understand how even simple vuilnerabilities, such as weak authentication or lack of encryption, can significantly increase security risks. it also reinforced the importance of layered security controls such as MFA, encryption, adn regular system updates.
